////Muscles - Pathology - Other findings

Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 08 - Soft tissue of Shoulder MRI
And I select the radio button 'Finding'
And I select 'Muscles' from the Finding dropdown

When I select 'Other findings' from Pathology dropdown menu
Then 'Add additionally pathology' button is enabled
And 'Fatty degeneration' checkbox is enabled
And 'Muscular hypotrophy' checkbox is enabled
And 'Muscular atrophy' checkbox is enabled
And 'Apophysitis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Fascial tear' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Muscular atrophy' checkbox
Then 'Complete' radio button is enabled
And 'Partial' radio button is enabled

When I select ' Fascial tear' checkbox
Then 'Muscle Herniation' checkbox is enabled
